      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COOL GENT (7) is progressing well with another good run, placing by one length (16.64) in a Maiden at this track. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Leading chance again. SOLAR POWER (5) turned in a good run last time, finishing in the placings (20.23) at Q Lakeside in a Grade 6. Lines up from box 5 for the first time. Goes very well here finding the frame in each of three starts. Form from her last run is proving strong. Can feature again. FLYING SERENA (1) is mixing form lately, finishing out of the placings last time at this track but was a Maiden winner two back at this track. Well placed here and can atone this time. LAKODA SKYLAH (2) looks an each-way chance.",
